############################################################ # Body ############################################################
BEGIN_PGML After a late night of math studying, you and your friends decide to go to your favorite tax-free fast food Mexican restaurant, _Burrito Chime_. You decide to order off of the dollar menu, which has 7 items. Your group has \$16 to spend (and will spend all of it). a. How many different orders are possible? Explain. (The _order_ in which the order is placed does not matter - just which and how many of each item that is ordered.)
